                        <interp inst="t18490101-name-200" type="given" value="CALEB EDWARD"></interp>CALEB EDWARD POWELL</persName>
                  </hi>. This half-crown and these two pieces are counterfeit.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
